# Example .npmrc configuration for publishing scoped packages
# Copy this to .npmrc and fill in your npm token

# Publish scoped packages as public
@nano402:registry=https://registry.npmjs.org/

# For CI/CD, use environment variable:
# //registry.npmjs.org/:_authToken=${NPM_TOKEN}

# For local publishing, you can use:
# //registry.npmjs.org/:_authToken=your-npm-token-here
# Or just run: npm login

